{"tid":592160,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"陳X佳","createTime":"2018-03-14T03:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T06:42:24.000Z","uid":48142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"773845c3c893a6d8b65ef987ebbd5f8b708c320b","tid":592160,"uid":48142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T03:59:28.000Z","msg":"香港女子潘曉穎的父親報案，指潘曉穎與她男友<span style=\"color: red;\">陳X佳</span>於2月13日赴台旅遊，但陳X佳獨自回港，潘女則下落不明。潘父在港報警。台北市警方隨後接獲香港警方通知尋找失蹤女子，遂翻查閉路電視片段，發現陳於2月17日獨自拖着粉紅色大型行李箱離開「紫園旅社」，形迹十分可疑。於是，台警將資料交予香港警方。台灣警方在晚上9時40分，於竹圍捷運站後方一處草皮尋獲女子遺體。"},{"pid":"82856af9a52d91a24bfe8468b16ed02fc1f10f55","tid":592160,"uid":78971,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T04:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/1BLVANIYoqk/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F1BLVANIYoqk%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=35ad3580&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9ff32cad2afb668afd7065839f4debf919bf557","tid":592160,"uid":175043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82856af9a52d91a24bfe8468b16ed02fc1f10f55","tid":592160,"uid":78971,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T04:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/1BLVANIYoqk/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F1BLVANIYoqk%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=35ad3580&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:42:24.000Z","msg":"hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}